Enum AttributeCode

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<AttributeCode>
      • constants.AttributeCode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EnumValue, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<AttributeCode>

    public enum AttributeCode
extends java.lang.Enum<AttributeCode>
implements EnumValue
    Attribute codes used in an Effect entry. They define the attribute set/mod by the effect (only if the effect type is "Alter Attribute").
    Author:
    MarcoForlini
